{"word":"ἐγχειρέω","slug":"ἐγχειρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐγχειρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χείρ'><el>χείρ</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to put one's hand in</i> or <i>to</i> a thing, <i>to attempt</i> it, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> rei, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to make an attempt</i> or <i>beginning</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to lay hands on, attack, assail</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}